Package: allocation
Type: Package
Title: Exact Optimal Allocation Algorithms for Stratified Sampling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Andrew M.", "Raim", email = "andrew.raim@census.gov",
        role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Tommy", "Wright", email = "Tommy.Wright@census.gov",
        role = c("aut")))
Description: 
    Implements several exact methods for allocating optimal sample sizes when
    designing stratified samples. These methods are discussed in
    <doi:10.1080/00031305.2012.733679> and <doi:10.1016/j.spl.2017.04.026>.
